name: Cyber Zombie 10,366
description:
artonomous portrait of Cyber
Zombie, a bitGAN created from the
burning of bitGANs (0o13) and (0o15).
This portrait was painted by an AI
enabled robot with 10,366
brushstrokes. It is a mystery why the
bitGANs have suddenly begun
appearing, though it appears that
they are trying to tell us something
important.
